<subSubSection id="659614BEFF84037A74C8CFE8FB06FA46" box="[199,1234,1420,1445]" pageId="10" pageNumber="67" type="etymology">
<paragraph id="2D334735FF84037A74C8CFE8FB06FA46" blockId="10.[151,1437,151,1445]" box="[199,1234,1420,1445]" pageId="10" pageNumber="67">
<emphasis id="1FF89B27FF84037A74C8CFE8FE92FA46" bold="true" box="[199,326,1420,1445]" pageId="10" pageNumber="67">Etymology</emphasis>
. This species is named after my beloved son, MaX. Name in genitive, invariable.
</paragraph>
